  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Value
    Generic interface for a variable value, that can be copied.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayVal
    Representation of an array of doubles.
    BooleanVal
    Representation of a boolean value.
    DoubleVal
    Representation of a double value
    NoneVal
    "None" value (describing the lack of value, or an empty assignment)
    SetVal
    Value that is defined as a set of values (with no duplicate elements).
    StringVal
    String value.
    ValueFactory
    Factory for creating variable values
